member.summary:
Binds a pipeline context tag to a named cache store. Place a List<CacheConfig> in InitialContext under the key "cache-config".
Each entry tells the cache processors: OutputTag — the context key they provide/require (matches Manifest.Provides[0] or Requires[0]) CacheName — the key used when reading/writing the ICacheStore (e.g. "dependency-graph") CacheStore — the store implementation to use
Example: new CacheConfig { OutputTag = "dep-graph", CacheName = "dependency-graph", CacheStore = new FileCacheStore(".modulus/cache") }
